import React from "react"; import classes from './DocCard.module.css'; const DocCard = props => (
{console.log(props.docInfo.docImg)}

{props.docInfo.name}

{props.docInfo.specialization .map( (sp, i) => i!=props.docInfo.specialization.length - 1 ? sp + ', ' : sp )}

{props.docInfo.education .map( (edu, i) => i!= props.docInfo.specialization.length - 1 ? edu.degree + ', ' : edu.degree)}

Wait Time

{props.docInfo.waitTime}

Experience

{props.docInfo.experience}

Wait Time

{((props.docInfo.satisfiedPatients)*100)+ '% ' + `(${props.docInfo.noOfReviews})`}

); export default DocCard
